 class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>Node.children</strong></code> 唯讀屬性會回傳一個 <code>Node</code> 之子<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"元素\"><code>元素</code></a>的動態（live）<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"語法","title":"語法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>children</em> = <em>node</em>.children;</pre>\n\n<p><code><em>children</em></code> 是一個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a>，為一個有順序性、由 <em><code>node</code></em> 中的 DOM 子元素所組成的集合。假如沒有子元素，則 <code><em>children</em></code> 內便不包含任何元素，且 <code>length</code> 為 <code>0</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tagName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill","title":"Polyfill","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Overwrites native 'children' prototype.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Adds Document &amp; DocumentFragment support for IE9 &amp; Safari.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Returns array instead of HTMLCollection.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>constructor <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n        constructor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n        constructor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">defineProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>constructor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'children'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token function-variable function\">get</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> node<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> nodes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>childNodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> children <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeType <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                        children<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> children<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Node <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Element<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"規範","title":"規範","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-parentnode-children\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"zh-TW\">The definition of 'ParentNode.children' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"瀏覽器相容性","title":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support (on <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>)</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.5\" title=\"Released on 2009-06-30.\">3.5</a> (1.9.1)</td>\n   <td>9.0 [1]</td>\n   <td>38.0</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Support on <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td>29.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/25\" title=\"Released on 2013-10-29.\">25.0</a> (25.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td>16.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Support on <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support (on <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.9.1)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Support on <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>25.0 (25.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td>16.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Internet Explorer 6, 7 and 8 supported it, but erroneously includes <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> nodes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/API/ParentNode\"><code>ParentNode</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/API/ChildNode\"><code>ChildNode</code></a> interfaces.</li>\n <li>\n  <div class=\"syntaxbox\" id=\"sect3\">Object types implementing this interface: <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, and <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a>.</div>\n </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"語法","id":"語法"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"Polyfill","id":"polyfill"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"Node.children 唯讀屬性會回傳一個 Node 之子元素的動態（live）HTMLCollection。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-tw/orphaned/web/api/parentnode/children","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/orphaned/web/api/parentnode/children/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn